sections.description: Create a Fake identities or just create your own about me description, creates a new widget that allow you to choose your diferent identities.
sections.installation:
This section describes how to install the plugin and get it working.

e.g.

  1. Upload “fake-about-me-fake” directory to “/wp-content/plugins/”

  2. Activate the plugin through the “Plugins” menu in WordPress

  3. Create a new Identity

  4. Add the Widget in your templates and configure
